Power can cast shadows, as it did
over the senate in my realm.$k$pThe prince and princess here,
however, remain radiant. May
they stay that way forever.

Oh! Do you have candy? I mean,
I am far from being a child and
care nothing for such things.$k$pBut if you have some, I wouldn't
say no.

You always strive to do so much
for everyone. And so I reward you
now with my thanks.

I have an older sister who I didn't
know about for years. But she
has become so precious to me.

I will now present to you my
full name—Sanaki Kirsch Altina.
I expect you will remember it.

You are standing in the presence
of Sanaki—37th Empress of Begnion.
You may kneel, if you wish.
It's only natural for the Apostle.

Average things can happen to
even the Apostle.

It's...a fluke. That's all. No
reason to fret.

What was that? I felt as if I just
transcended in some way!

You stand in the presence of Sanaki,
Empress of Begnion! I am the
Apostle—the voice of the goddess!

Hmpf. I seem to have grown while
here in this world. Have you
noticed any differences?$k$pI mean, avert your eyes! You gaze
upon the Empress of Begnion!
I am a privilege to behold!$k$pAnd yet, you don't give a fig for all
that, do you? You stand in my
presence without fear.$k$pMost would beg my permission to
approach. But not you. I must say
that I find it...refreshing.$k$pStill, I am not a commoner, and
though I seem to be a girl like
any other, I am not.$k$pI don't have the luxury of acting
juvenile. But when I'm with
you, I wish I did.$k$pI think you might be a bad
influence on me. How curious.
I wonder what it means...$k$pStill, never forget who I am—the
Empress of Begnion!
えいっ！
これっ！
きゃああっ！
Lout!
There's no stopping me!
I won't tolerate this!
What treachery!
How tiresome.
Sorry...
Heh
Here you are, engaging with me so...casually!
Ahhh! Pardon? Scared? I think you mean someone else.
You stand in the presence of Sanaki, Empress of Begnion.
Ha ha ha! Every moment with you is amusing.
A summoner, you say? How wonderful—the stuff of fairy tales!
The truth is...I cannot hear the goddess's voice...
You may have the great honor of remaining at my side.
Very well.
What next?
Amusing.
